458a","position":"1784844427318420001-6f8a882e-d9b4-401c-9e25-0e103bd93c77"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"},{"content_hash":"f60952664413f647486943db68649f8c1413d0fef218aaa4d8e096761430a974","event_uuid":"f55545d2-9468-43c9-89cd-f469fe3ca1c2","position":{"commit_sha":"93448f32fbd64a752bbef9fc1dd533a0c618c6f2","position":"1784847799680294001-f55545d2-9468-43c9-89cd-f469fe3ca1c2"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":null,"claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":null,"comments":[{"author":"RebarBotNava","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Test contract frozen before code: authoritative contract is the ticket AC (lizard imported through guard_import(extra=\"metrics\"), per-function and per-file/aggregate true CCN over Python plus one non-Python source, and OptionalDependencyError becomes Unavailable). Preconditions: real temp repo contains Python and JavaScript functions with branch-derived CCN; missing-extra path forces guard_import to raise. Production path: public lizard_complexity.analyze(repo_root) with real lizard for polyglot E2E and a guarded import seam for absence. Tier: unit for deterministic aggregation plus in-process E2E through real lizard because a fake one tier lower cannot prove polyglot parsing. Observable postconditions: deterministic repo-relative function records, file totals and global total/max; exact Unavailable reason/accruing_since. Negative control: straight-line functions remain CCN 1 while branching functions are CCN 2. CI gate: make test (tests must execute, no skip). Stateful collateral/recovery/fault injection: N/A; analyzer is read-only.","timestamp":1784844165542240001},{"author":"RebarBotNava","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Held-out validation: standard-tier independent implementer completed in 1 attempt and saw only tests/unit/metrics/test_lizard_complexity.py. Restored edge/E2E oracle: 4/4 tests green, including real lizard parsing Python + JavaScript, exact OptionalDependencyError -> Unavailable, and empty aggregate. Mutation changed every reported CCN to 1; the held-out polyglot test failed on per-function, per-file, total, and max values, then passed after restoration. Refactoring litmus passes: assertions use only public analyze output and would survive private helper extraction/renaming. Dev extra now includes metrics so the real-lizard test executes in gating CI while plain/core install stays lean.","timestamp":1784844427318420001},{"author":"RebarBotNava","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Final local verification green: make lint; make typecheck (375 source files); make test (7,071 passed, 29 skipped, 113 deselected). Five-axis review: no blocking correctness/readability/architecture/security/performance findings; adapter is 71 LOC and deterministic. Initial full run exposed one pre-existing ambient assumption in grounding coverage; the test now explicitly forces no-tool, its exact node passed, and the complete rerun is green.","timestamp":1784847799680294001}],"created_at":1784517467309831001,"creation_channel":"cli","deps":[{"link_uuid":"3458f38b-dcc2-402d-bc35-4f7d05018f05","relation":"depends_on","target_id":"9597-1b85-d2ab-4eed"},{"link_uuid":"22480c26-dc6c-4373-b995-74e9ae4f4ffb","relation":"depends_on","target_id":"e7a0-acef-ec67-42bb"},{"link_uuid":"1231682b-0703-4619-8ab1-bdf1691a7117","relation":"depends_on","target_id":"3b30-2168-ba16-41fc"}],"description":"## Description\nComplexity analyzer using lizard (pip dep from the `[metrics]` extra) for real per-function cyclomatic complexity (CCN) across ~25 languages, populating `AnalyzerResult.complexity`.\n\n## Review-driven corrections\n- lizard is used AS AN IMPORTED LIBRARY here (via `guard_import(extra=\"metrics\")`), not shelled — `guard_import` raises `OptionalDependencyError`; CATCH it and return `Unavailable(reason, accruing_since)`, not bare ImportError.\n- Live in `src/rebar/metrics/analyzers/` (not `adapters/`).\n- Uses the interface/AnalyzerResult from 3b30 and the scan root from e7a0; deps are sibling stories.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- [ ] `analyzers/lizard_complexity.py` runs lizard over the scan root -> per-file/aggregate CCN (optionally token/param counts).\n- [ ] Extra not installed -> `OptionalDependencyError` caught -> Unavailable(reason, accruing_since).\n- [ ] Exercised on Python + one non-Python fixture (contributes toward the epics cross-language AC).\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] Unit over Python + one other language fixture; guard-absent -> Unavailable.\n\n## Dependencies: 3b30, 9597, e7a0 (siblings). Recorded edges: depends_on 9597, e7a0.\n## Files likely touched: src/rebar/metrics/analyzers/lizard_complexity.py (new), tests/unit/metrics/test_lizard_complexity.py (new)\n## Estimated scope: M","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[{"path":"src/rebar/metrics/analyzers/lizard_complexity.py","reason":"new: lizard CCN via guard_import(extra=metrics); OptionalDependencyError -> Unavailable"},{"path":"tests/unit/metrics/test_lizard_complexity.py","reason":"new: Python + one non-Python fixture; guard-absent -> Unavailable"}],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[["depends_on","3b30-2168-ba16-41fc"],["depends_on","9597-1b85-d2ab-4eed"],["depends_on","e7a0-acef-ec67-42bb"],[